caption:
“Somebody pinch me! That’s ME!”

Vivian saw the billboard. Then she stood in front of it. And in that moment, everything this campaign stands for — self-love, pride, power — came to life.

“This is beyond words and my wildest dreams… To be an arch image for self-love, self-confidence and blissful lingerie is so incredibly special.”

Let this be your reminder: embrace your body with love and pride. You deserve nothing less. #BodyLoveProject
